# .env.local — LOCAL DEV ONLY
# ============================================================
# Production deployments read env vars from Vercel directly (those are
# stored as "Sensitive" in the dashboard — Vercel decrypts them at runtime
# but the CLI cannot retrieve them, which is why `vercel env pull` returns
# blanks). This file is for running the app locally via `npm start` or
# `vercel dev` ONLY.
#
# This file is .gitignored — never commit it.
# Update each key by pasting from the source URLs in the comments below.
# Maintain this file manually — DO NOT run `vercel env pull` again, it'll
# wipe everything back to blanks.
# ============================================================

# ---------- Claude Haiku (card recognition) ----------
# Get from: https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=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

# ---------- Google Cloud Vision (reverse-image + DON ranking) ----------
